snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Brother Nitin Rao Ji... what happened in PULWAMA, is the Handi.Work of FEW PERSONS... Which is Condemnable and Liable to be CRITICIZED by ALL... PEACE LOVING CITIZENS of BOTH HINDUSTAN and PAKISTAN.... everyone of US feeling Concerned and Bitter about those Brave Soldiers, belonging to POOR people.. Risking their lives to Make Both ends meet and Earning their SALARIES for their Families.... they told their families that they will return Home, after a Hard Day's work....
"Zara yaad UNHEN bhi kar lo, Jo LAUT ke GHAR naa Aye.....Aye Mere VATAN ke logo, Zara AANKH me bhar lo Paani, Jo SHAHEED huye hai UN kee Zara yaad karo QURBANI....
But the Politicians and all Parties are Concerned ONLY for the Political Mileage, THEY can GET from this TRAGEDY of more than 40 Valuable lives of Trained Soldiers...NO Political Leader or Party is at present WORRIED about the poor souls lost in the Pulwama Attack.... but are making out PLANS...how to WIN the Forthcoming Elections of 2019... with an Eye on the Vote.Bank..but the Right Thinking people of both countries are Worried about the LOOMING WAR clouds, Gathering on the Sky, with VULTURES circling about the Common Sky of Both India and Pakistan... waiting to dive-in for their PRAY...
We salute the brave soldiers.... and pray that No War Should be Thrusted upon the common people...
PUNJAB and KASHMIR are holding their breaths, to know about the Result of the present CRISIS....
May the Almighty grant Sense to our Leaders and not to lose Sanity to Declare WAR....
More Mothers are likely to lose their SONS in case the War is THRUSTED upon us.....
